snippet.title: Johnny Depp, Amber Heard, Juliette Lewis, Kaley Cuoco & MORE on Art Of Elysium Red Carpet!
snippet.description:
The Golden Globes may reign as the weekend's biggest fashion display in Hollywood, but the Art of Elysium Heaven Gala comes in at a very close (and stylish) second. 

Johnny Depp is dapper, while his wife Amber Heard is red hot in a sexy slip dress. Juliette Lewis donned a dramatic dress that looked as if it escaped from a Tim Burton film. Kaley Cuoco kept it cool and conservative in a white jumpsuit. 

Another notable attendees included  Kaley Cuoco, Zendaya,  Malin Akerman and Bella Thorne in a very revealing cleavage popping outfit
